policy.generated
plan-shape:
- ClientContext::base_policy(vars, auth, ctx)
- inherited scope policy layers are applied once
- endpoint policy layer is applied once
- runtime policy layer is final
- ensure_accept(response content type) unless HEAD/no-content
- policy.into_parts()
- rate_limit.canonicalize()
- ResolvedPolicy { headers, query, timeout, auth, retry, rate_limit }
